column12: ni li suli tawa mi: nanpa wan la, seli li pona tawa mi. a seli li ken tan ken mute. nanpa tu la kulupu pi jan ale li pona mute. ken pi kulupu ni li suli a! nasin sona ona en kalama muisi ona li ken pona e ale. mi ale li tan sona pi jan mute. jan wan li ken pali lili tawa pali suli. jan o pali kepeken kulupu. nanpa tu la sina ale li pona mute mute. mi toki e pona tawa sina. pali sina pi kulupu LSW li musi li sin li pali pona li lon e pilin pona tawa mi. sina pona.

toki ali lon ma li jo e ijo sama mute: ki ken toki e wile sona. mi ken toki e ijo pi jo mi. mi ken toki e pali pi wile mi tawa jan. taso, namako la, toki mi li jo e ijo ante mute: jan pi toki Kanse li ken ala pilin e ma pi kipisi tawa nimi "un" tawa nimi "une" pi kipisi tawa mije tawa meli. taso ni la, jan pi toki Eso li jo e nimi ijo lili wan tawa jan mije tawa jan meli: nimi "tema". toki Kipa (toki pi ma Oselija) la ijo li ken mije anu meli ante ante - anu kili.

toki ali li pana e sona pi jan ona. lipu Mi Lukin E Soweli la jan pi sona toki Alesanta Akenwa li tawa ma kasi telo pi weka tawa jan e mi li tawa tomo sona nanpa tu wan pi ma Amelika pi poka pi ma Kalalinula e mi tan ni: ona li wile pana e sona pi suli nimi pi suli pi ken pi toki pi tan sona - pi kama lon tenpo ni: toki li weka lon tenpo ali.

column9: It is back and somewhat foreground text in a digital drawing. A poster, a busstop sign, and on a blue desk
column12:
There is a digital drawing in 4 point perspective based on the Golden Spiral composition. The drawing's main focus is a mirror which takes up 2/3 showcasing a large part of an empty dark cool colored room. with nylon floors and a carpet. There is a girl as the main focus who is dressed in alternative or goth-like clothing (a black skirt with a 2nd semitransparent black skirt over it, a black belt, and multiple semi-see through tops layered on each other.) She is holding a phone which is creating an infinte mirror effect within the opened camera app.
Behind her is an obscured poster in Sitelen Pona saying "o weka sama sitelen lon ma ko" and on her desk is written "ni li sitelen ala sitelen" referecing her having drawn it on the desk with a marker to test if it writes on the desk. Outside of the mirror is a window showing a red and white bus and two buildings and a concret path with hedges at early dusk. In front of the bus but behind the hedges is a typical blue road sign that says "ma tomo" on the largest plate, and "kekesan" below it in white writting. Below the window is a small multi-leveled black metal nightstand, which is holding a 5 cent coin in the shape of the Sitelen Pona for mani, Toki Pona: The Language of Good, a typical black chocker, two tickets, a fuzzy worm on a string toy, and the all new DougDoug MugMug.

column12: jan Majeka has written as the title for a Biology assignment "sona sijelo  pi pali sona   #1,5    insa ilo sijelo kon", a date "tenpo: musi / sona   sike 2023" (likely the beginning of the school year, musi being used as a reference to the Summer break and sona as a reference to the school year), and the subject marker "sona sijelo" to let her know that she is writting notes for Biologie because she had to use a couple of her notebooks for more than one subject. As a note she has written "ilo insa sijelo kon li lukin e sike moku pi soweli insa" (likely supposed to be "lukin sama sike" as she wrote this only a month into her Toki Pona learning). Underneath that she has written "pali lili :" (likely meaning assignments) with her answers to the assignment about smog and the atmosphere effecting the respetory system (ilo insa sijelo kon "air-related inner body organs").

column12: In the photo are 3 diagrams of different filtering techniques. In the top left is distilling, where the dirt is shown with ma acting as a pictogram instead of saying dirt/aard, and telo for water. In the top right is filtering, with ma being again a pictogram in place of dirt/aard. On the bottom center is extraheren, lete is being used as a pictogram for sugar, ma for dirt/aard residue and telo for water.

column12:
tenpo kulupu li weka la mi pilin anpa a.
tenpo Monday la tomo tawa kijetesantakalu (Wolverine) li kepeken tenpo pi suli ike tan pakala nasin tan pakala ilo. tenpo pi sike tu la mi tawa tomo la telo mute li kama tan sewi. wawa kin li lon sewi.
tenpo Tuesday la mi pali lon tomo Panpu pi ma Royal Oak. mi moku ala e misikeke la telo jaki mute li kama tan nena mi. anpa a. kin la pali li utala li nasa e sona kulupu.
tenpo Wednesday li tenpo Juneteenth la mi pali mani ala. tomo ilo la mi telo e jaki pi supa noka. mi alasa pana e ilo lete kon lon lupa pi tomo pali mi. taso ilo lete li pakala. mi ken pona e ilo taso lon tenpo pi seli ike ala. poka pi pini suno la tenpo musi Ferndale Bike Night li lon. mi tawa ni kepeken ilo wawa pi sike tu. mi musi pona li kama sona e jan pona Eaton e jan pona Fritz e kulupu meli pi ilo tawa wawa. kulupu ilo li pini la mi tawa esun moku Kroger pi ma Royal Oak. ilo mani li utala mute e mi li lanpan e tenpo suli. kin la mi o pana e telo wawa lon poki ilo. mi ni la tenpo li 22:15 anu sama. telo mute a li kama tan sewi. taso mi awen tawa. mi anpa ala e mi e ilo. taso len mi li kama telo mute.
tenpo Thursday la mi pilin pakala mute lon sijelo. tan seli anu tan jaki anu tan pakala lawa la mi sona ala. mi o lape taso. mi ken ala pali. mi awen lon supa anpa taso.
tenpo pimeja la mii lape lon tenpo suli
tenpo ni la Friday 10:15 la mi awen pali mani ala. sijelo li kama pilin pona lili. tan lape suli
seli li awen lon tomo lon kon. mi o pakala ala tan seli

column12:
musi Anapi
musi Anapi li musi lipu tan jan Antuwa Posa. jan li musi lon poka jan ante. kon musi li ni(Di): jan li jan seli. ona li pakala
e kasi kule seli. tenpo lon la ona li wile lili e kasi seli ni. jan ale li musi kulupu. ona li wile e kama sama. jan ale li pini pona kulupu
li pini ike kulupu

ijo musi
lipu kasi kule seli 50. ona li Ku5
 lipu kule 1 10 li jo e nanpa ni: 1 1 1 2 2 3 3 4 4 5
 sike sona 8. laso.
 sike pakala 3. loje.

wile jan
musi Anapi li musi kulupu. jan ale li wile e kama sama. jan ale li wile lon supa e lipu kepeken nasin pi nanpa ona. tenpo open la
jan li lon e lipu nanpa lili. tenpo pini la jan li lon e lipu nanpa suli.
jan li ken ala lukin e lipu lon luka ona. jan li ken lukin e lipu lon luka pi  jan ante taso. ni: la jan li wile pana e sona tawa jan ante. ona li ken kepeken
e sona ni tawa musi lili. jan li lon pona e lipu mute la kulupu li kama jo e nanpa pona mute.

pali open
o lon supa e sike sona 8. sitelen ona o lon sewi. o lon supa e sike pakala 3. sitelen sina o lon anpa. kulupu li jo e sike ni:
sitelen lon sike ni li lon sewi. kulupu li jo ala e sike ni: sitelen lon sike ni li lon anpa
o ante e kulupu lipu 50. jan li wile sona e nasin lipu lon insa ona. o pana e lipu mute tawa jan ale
 jan 2 anu jan 3 li musi la jan ale li kama jo e lipu 5.
 jan 4 aun jan 5 li musi la jan ale li kama jo e lipu 5.
SULI la jan li ken ala lukina e lipu lon luka. jan li kama jo e lipu ona kepeken nasin ni: monsi lipu li lukin e jan ante.
lipu ante li lon kulupu lon supa. sinpin ona li lon anpa. o alasa e jan nanpa wan. ona li open musi.

musi musi
jan li pini e tenpo musi ona la jan lon poka soto ona li open e tenpo musi. jan li jo e tenpo musi la ona li pali e pali wan tan ni:
 #1 o pana e sona tawa jan ante
 #2 o weka e lipu tan luka sina
 #3 o lon supa e lipu tan luka sina
jan li ken ala pali e ala. ona li pali e pali wan taso
SULI LA jan li ken ala pana e sona tawa jan ante lon tenpo musi pi jan ante. ona li pana e sona. taso la onali ken toki e sona luka jan

tomo suli Sikansija pi ma Ate
lon suno mun musi pi tenpo suwi selo pi ma Sala laso ale la tomo suli li lape.
tomo lape li lukin e tomo pi monsi ona e kulupu sinpin la ona li pona.
jan li insa ni la kulupu suli li kama sinpin ni li pana e lukin monsuta
toki li kalama wawa. pali ala li tawa mi. mi o sama wile sewi. meli o pakala.
ma ale li lukin ale utala li pana e telo mute tan wile moli ala tan weka moku ale.
taso kalama utala a pi kulupu pkala la o kute e melil wan suwi tawa ale jan.
ona suwi li lukin ale suli. ken ala li tawa mi. mi o moli tawa sewi tawa ma Ate mi. kon li tan kiwen. tawa sewi li open e kalama musi moli. ma li loje moli.
suno la ale li laso. pan li tan ma ale. moku en musi taso li lon ma Ate.
tan ni la mun musi pi tenpo suwi selo pi ma Sale laso ale la tomo suli li lape.
